{"tid":612860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社北京　港澳辦：戴耀廷等港獨分子　不准聯合　不准找外援　不准越我等底線","createTime":"2018-04-01T07:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T07:58:29.000Z","uid":47714,"like":45,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"27650a7f1d4b4bccc202c3c8d0d9767174bf176b","tid":612860,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2018-03/31/c_1122620087.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Fpolitics%2F2018-03%2F31%2Fc_1122620087.htm&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=4f0be907\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2018-03/31/c_1122620087.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n　　新華社北京3月31日電　國務院港澳事務辦公室發言人31日針對戴耀廷等個別&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;分子在台灣鼓吹&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;言論事發表談話，表示堅決支持香港特別行政區政府依法規管&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;分子與外部分裂勢力的勾連活動。<br />\n<br />\n　　該發言人表示，我們注意到香港大學法律系副教授戴耀廷最近到台灣參加&ldquo;台獨&rdquo;組織舉辦的有關會議並公然鼓吹&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;等言論的動向，並註意到香港特別行政區政府對此予以強烈譴責的有關表態。我們認為，香港極少數人勾結外部分裂勢力，公然宣揚所謂香港&ldquo;獨立建國&rdquo;等言論，充分暴露了其分裂國家的企圖，嚴重違反國家憲法、香港基本法和香港現行有關法律，是對&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;底線的挑戰，對此類活動絕不能置若罔聞、縱容姑息。我們堅決主張並支持香港特別行政區政府依法規管&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;分子與外部分裂勢力的勾連活動，以切實維護國家主權和安全，維護香港的長期繁榮穩定和香港社會的根本利益。"},{"pid":"99ced336e44cc6a3de6aa10f8aed9d40de996b07","tid":612860,"uid":83582,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"驚到瀨屎咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f181a51fdc898468a31348e1d1ff6ab64e574b","tid":612860,"uid":49392,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"跟住點?又話犯法又講唔出邊條"},{"pid":"769c8fb2a2dd4a0973d14a12be65283134729c88","tid":612860,"uid":142405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"佔領中環正式啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269930c2a38561bf1244505f5e42ac0877ff7fea","tid":612860,"uid":142405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:05:33.000Z","msg":"[img]<img src=\"http://cdn.makeagif.com/media/6-26-2015/idhEp5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F6-26-2015%2FidhEp5.gif&h=f3e2976f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08ca8257b870ae76965041cad25ddc5a4d57746a","tid":612860,"uid":43398,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"原來台灣等於外部？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁口交部之前又講台灣係&ldquo;不可分割既一部份&rdquo;既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f3e4270dc05537aa8c3dc6f7d634c7f2df8c3a","tid":612860,"uid":93784,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"人地係台灣UP乜都得架啦<br />\n言論自由黎架屌你老母共產黨<br />\n又搞白色恐怖 而家係威脅緊港台<br />\n最後就係想人思想上自我審查"},{"pid":"58aed3547bec3d31ffaf15b19f11b350ff47a235","tid":612860,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7579310ca6c011d1eb3699017b417888a11ba9","tid":612860,"uid":47359,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"唔聽話=港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1790f89abed8e1ca626d7ab54be805e4d519f83a","tid":612860,"uid":48964,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:50:29.000Z","msg":"官方咁大反應，反證戴今次做得啱，方向正確"},{"pid":"b14f7a5aa0b4413d02ca4f905c3319161be43796","tid":612860,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1790f89abed8e1ca626d7ab54be805e4d519f83a","tid":612860,"uid":48964,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyT